# kleopatra is the KDE/GnuPG certificate manager; only autostart it on the KDE
# targets. Detection mirrors the fcitx5/solaar templates: GNOME-only means
# gnome-shell on PATH without plasmashell; with neither desktop (headless,
# container, CI) the KDE variant renders and it keeps deploying.
{{ if and (eq .chezmoi.os "linux") (lookPath "gnome-shell") (not (lookPath "plasmashell")) -}}
kleopatra.desktop
{{ end }}
